name beamer-varbox
category Package
revision 78996
shortdesc Provide beamer boxes with variable size corners
longdesc This package provides beamer boxes with variable size corners.
longdesc It scales the corner arc of a beamer block relative to the
longdesc standard rounded predefined option provided by the beamer
longdesc class. The package depends on beamer and xkeyval.
